<sup>3</sup>, <a href='https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/?term="Namdari%20S"[Author]' class="usa-link" aria-describedby="id7"><span class="name western">Surena Namdari</span></a><div hidden="hidden" id="id7">
<h3><span class="name western">Surena Namdari</span></h3>
<div class="p">
<sup>3</sup>The
Rothman Institute of Orthopaedics at Thomas
Jefferson University Hospitals, Philadelphia, USA</div>
<div class="p">Find articles by <a href='https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/?term="Namdari%20S"[Author]' class="usa-link"><span class="name western">Surena Namdari</span></a>
